{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467830/extras/banner1.png?t=1617004273\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u201cWhy do we have to look like trees? I just want to be me.\u201d</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Overview</h2><strong>An adventure game about SIIMI, who set out on a journey to discover her true \u2018me\u2019.</strong><br>SIIMI is a puzzle game designed as a criticism of the unnatural standards placed upon us in our appearance-oriented society. The objective of the game is removing leaves from the main character. Siimi, the protagonist of this game, dreams of a world where she doesn\u2019t have to look pretty in a world where values are decided by looks.<br><br><strong>Can SIIMI\u2019s little journey create a wave to change the world?</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Characteristics</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A story about loving oneself, regardless of how society treats you.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Various characters with their own stories to tell.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Art-style portraying a vast, but warm desert.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Heart-warming lyrical soundtrack.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467830/extras/Artwork1.png?t=1617004273\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">&quot;Begin your journey in the desert with Siimi to find her true identity.&quot;</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Story</h2>SIIMI is a member of the Mi tribe inhabiting a desert village. \u201cMi\u201ds live with Yggdrami, the sacred tree. They imitate Yggdrami and aspire to look better than what they are. However, SIIMI is an outcast because she is bad at making herself look beautiful. SIIMI eventually grew tired of trying to keep up with standards she could never match. She decided to stop imitating Yggdrami and left the village to find her true identity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What awaits Siimi at the end of the desert?</h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Siimi got a car! Pick me up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/e360194087a4d8669c2958e471db81bc33a46a1d.jpg"},{"name":"Other way to use the straightener","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/6aaca05c157582567248ea739150b83745fa7c2a.jpg"},{"name":"Help the flowers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/1028d1f00f43058c2aceeff84da299c0dd94fedc.jpg"},{"name":"\"Knock knock. Is anyone there?\"","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/10853e8771180912aad0a839e7e6594f2d49836f.jpg"},{"name":"To Village Exterior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/57561a640c3ea21028575bc2788d1f7c2f0c2200.jpg"},{"name":"Art Critic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/3fd2077ff6e551e2aadac2bdbce77ffa614952ab.jpg"},{"name":"Counting Numbers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/783e19cb178eaeb2f5d3d2129d43844eed7341d8.jpg"},{"name":"The Best Leaf Tea","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/aa39a24e299f14c34ecbcabf34aa672a78a0976b.jpg"},{"name":"Kaboom!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/e8b9f8de12e01dc63a9bf5cb6ea15080d8767b42.jpg"},{"name":"Giant\u2019s Sad Secret","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467830/b71c71c71a78973c8f730657ea8eda8de01717ee.jpg"}],"total":20},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467830/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1617004273","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467830/page.bg.jpg?t=1617004273","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass